data.description: Welcome to this charming 35-acre property nestled in the heart of tranquility. This unique estate offers not one, but two homes, making it an ideal retreat for multi-generational living or potential income generation. The primary residence is an adorable wood cabin featuring a wrap-around deck, with above ground pool built into the deck, and a second-story porch, allowing you to soak in the stunning views of the surrounding landscape. Inside, you'll find two cozy bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a convenient half bath. The cabin also boasts an unfinished office space, perfect for remote work or creative endeavors. This home has seen partial remodeling, blending modern comfort with rustic charm, and ready for your finishing touches!The second home, a single-wide, offers two bedrooms and one bathroom, making it an excellent option for rental income or guest accommodations. The possibilities are endless with this additional living space.For those with an equestrian passion, the property is partially fenced and equipped with a large barn featuring three stalls, providing a haven for your horses, cattle, or your homesteading dreams. Multiple storage shed, above ground pool.
